學習規範 Course Policy
	    This is a demanding course in which you will learn the theoretical foundations and applications of Quantum Mechanics. 
This is a challenging physics course, and you must conduct yourself as a serious and responsible adult student during the course.
This means taking responsibility for your own education, attending all the lectures, paying close attention in class, spending considerable amount of time outside of class hours completing the exercises and revising the material.      

