課程概述 Course Description
       由基本公設出發，建立量子力學架構，並介紹其相關重要應用。
Start from quantum mechanical axioms, illustrate the main concepts of quantum mechanics, and introduce related important topics.
Start from quantum mechanical axioms, illustrate the main concepts of quantum mechanics, and introduce related important topics.
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Equip students with knowledge and understanding of Quantum MechanicsEquip students with understanding of framework essential to Modern PhysicsEquip students with foundations of numerous applications in modern technologies 

